    warrant:hasSoftwareVersion "0359377-03.02" ;
    warrant:hasDescription "FAR-22X8 series. Interfaces: LAN (S-band Radar, ECDIS); SERIAL (GPS, Gyrocompass, Speedlog, AIS); VIDEO (VDR). Access: service engineer only, authorization codes required. FMEA: settings modified Sev=6, Prob=6, Det=3, RPN=108." .

